# Session [28] – Network+

## Main Topics
- IDS chist?  
- IPS chist?  
- Tarze kar Intrusion Detection / Intrusion Prevention  
- Estefadeh-ha dar network  

## Flashback – IDS/IPS Basics
- **IDS (Intrusion Detection System)** → detect mikonad har activity shak-dar, attack, unauthorized access  
- **IPS (Intrusion Prevention System)** → ham detect mikonad ham جلوی حمله ro migirad  
- IDS = passive  
- IPS = active & inline  

## Explanation

### IDS (Intrusion Detection System)
- Traffic ro monitor mikonad  
- Attack ro tashkhis mide  
- **Action:** فقط alert, log, notification  
- No blocking  

### IPS (Intrusion Prevention System)
- Traffic ro inline check mikonad  
- Attack ro detect + block mikonad  
- **Action:** drop packet, reset connection, block IP  

### NIDS / NIPS (Network-Based)
- Traffic network ro check mikonad  
- Baraye LAN, WAN, datacenter  

### HIDS / HIPS (Host-Based)
- Activity system (processes, files, logs) ro monitor mikonad  
- Baraye servers / PCs sensitive  

### Example Table
| System | Meaning | Function | Action |
|--------|---------|----------|--------|
| IDS | Intrusion Detection System | Detect | Alert / Log |
| IPS | Intrusion Prevention System | Detect + Prevent | Block / Drop |
| NIDS | Network IDS | Monitor traffic | Alert |
| NIPS | Network IPS | Analyze + block inline | Block |
| HIDS | Host IDS | Monitor host | Alert |
| HIPS | Host IPS | Prevent host attacks | Block |

### Estefadeh-ha
- Stop DDoS  
- Detect malware patterns  
- Block port scans  
- Protection baraye datacenter & enterprise  

